							<body  ><div class="section"><p class="VoteReason">A party vote was called for on the question,<em> That the </em><em>Policing (Cost Recovery) Amendment Bill be now read a second time.</em></p><p class="VoteCount"><strong>Ayes 63</strong></p><p class="VoteText">New Zealand National 59; Māori Party 2; ACT New Zealand 1; United Future 1.</p><p class="VoteCount"><strong>Noes 56</strong></p><p class="VoteText">New Zealand Labour 32; Green Party 13; New Zealand First 11.</p><p class="VoteResult">Bill read a second time.</p></div></body>
